你有一定的文学基础。

1282
01:14:50,060 --> 01:14:54,200
Right? And then when it becomes an empire, it's forced to have a vista.
然后当它成为帝国时，必须拥有视野。

1283
01:14:54,640 --> 01:14:59,140
It's forced to have, like, a global perspective. And
它必须拥有一种全球视野。然后

1284
01:14:59,140 --> 01:15:02,280
this change from a nation or
从民族或

1285
01:15:02,280 --> 01:15:05,240
coherent people into a cosmopolitan empire,
统一的人群转变为世界性帝国，

1286
